OL,3,CScotland becoming more intolerant amid
OL,4,Cimmigration debate, warns Yousaf
OL,6,FScotland is becoming more intolerant
OL,7,Fas "toxicity" around the immigration
OL,8,Fdebate spreads north of the border,
OL,9,Fformer first minister Humza Yousaf has
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FHe told a new BBC documentary that
OL,13,Fpoliticians have not engaged enough
OL,14,Fwith genuine concerns around
OL,15,Fimmigration.
OL,17,FResearch from the think tank Migration
OL,18,FPolicy Scotland, shared with the
OL,19,Fprogramme, suggested opinions on
OL,20,Fimmigration are "cooling".
