OL,3,CScotland becoming more intolerant amid
OL,4,Cimmigration debate, warns Yousaf
OL,6,FReform UK's Richard Tice also said the
OL,7,Fpublic are "questioning what they've
OL,8,Fbeen told by politicians" on the issue.
OL,10,FThe radio documentary, titled Scotland
OL,11,FWants You, examines whether Scotland
OL,12,Fis more open to migrants than other
OL,13,Fparts of the UK.
OL,15,FMr Yousaf was first minister for just
OL,16,Fover a year until he stood down in May
OL,17,F2024.
OL,19,FThe SNP politician was the first
OL,20,FScottish Asian and Muslim to serve in
OL,21,Fthe country's highest elected role.
