OL,3,CScotland becoming more intolerant amid
OL,4,Cimmigration debate, warns Yousaf
OL,6,FHe was a frequent critic of the then
OL,7,FConservative UK government's
OL,8,Fimmigration policy ` branding the
OL,9,FRwanda deportation plan "morally
OL,10,Frepugnant".
OL,12,FSpeaking to the documentary, Mr Yousaf
OL,13,Ftook issue with the phrase "we're all
OL,14,FJock Tamson's bairns" ` the suggestion
OL,15,Fthat everyone is welcome in Scotland.
OL,17,FHe said: "The idea we're all Jock
OL,18,FTamson's Bairns is a very nice
OL,19,Fsoundbite, and one that I've used on
OL,20,Fplenty of occasions in the past.
