OL,3,CScotland becoming more intolerant amid
OL,4,Cimmigration debate, warns Yousaf
OL,6,F"We use these soundbites to perhaps
OL,7,Fmask the fact that people have genuine
OL,8,Fconcerns about immigration ` but I
OL,9,Fwould suggest misplaced concerns."
OL,11,FMr Yousaf added: "I have to say, in
OL,12,Frecent months and over the past couple
OL,13,Fof years, it is a feeling that the
OL,14,Ftoxicity of the debate around
OL,15,Fimmigration and multiculturalism has
OL,16,Fmanaged to find its way up here.
