OL,3,CScotland becoming more intolerant amid
OL,4,Cimmigration debate, warns Yousaf
OL,6,F"Scotland I'm afraid, of course, is
OL,7,Fbecoming more intolerant ` both in the
OL,8,Fpublic space and frankly I've seen
OL,9,Fsome of that intolerance in the
OL,10,Fpolitical space too."
OL,12,FSarah Kyambi from Migration Policy
OL,13,FScotland has overseen research on
OL,14,FScottish attitudes for the past three
OL,15,Fyears.She told the programme:
OL,16,F"Scottish attitudes to immigration are
OL,17,Fcooling.
OL,19,F"More people want to see the level of
OL,20,Fimmigration reduced than they did last
OL,21,Fyear or the year before
