OL,3,CScotland becoming more intolerant amid
OL,4,Cimmigration debate, warns Yousaf
OL,6,F"That cooling is from a point when we
OL,7,Ffirst started the survey ` a point
OL,8,Fwhen the largest cohort in our survey
OL,9,Fwanted to see an increase in
OL,10,Fimmigration.
OL,12,F"But now the level of support for
OL,13,Fimmigration reduction are increasing.
OL,15,F"I think there is a narrative about
OL,16,Fwhere Scotland sits on immigration
OL,17,Fthat I worry leads to a kind of
OL,18,Fcomplacency.
