OL,3,CScotland becoming more intolerant amid
OL,4,Cimmigration debate, warns Yousaf
OL,6,F"The idea that there is an inherent
OL,7,Fgreater positivity amongst the
OL,8,FScottish policy towards immigration is
OL,9,Flikely to be mistaken."
OL,11,FThe think tank holds regular surveys
OL,12,Fon the issue, and it heard from more
OL,13,Fthan 2,300 people across all of
OL,14,FScotland in February last year.
OL,16,FIn May, immigration entered the list
OL,17,Fof Scots' top five concerns for the
OL,18,Ffirst time, according to the separate
OL,19,FUnderstanding Scotland Economy Tracker
OL,20,Ffrom the Diffley Partnership and the
OL,21,FDavid Hume Institute.
