OL,3,CScotland becoming more intolerant amid
OL,4,Cimmigration debate, warns Yousaf
OL,6,FReform's Mr Tice said attitudes are
OL,7,Fhardening because people are not
OL,8,Ffeeling better off.
OL,10,FHe told the programme: "Scottish
OL,11,Fpeople are concerned by some of the
OL,12,Fimpact of illegal immigration and too
OL,13,Fmuch legal immigration.
OL,15,F"People are questioning what they've
OL,16,Fbeen told by politicians.
OL,18,F"They're saying: I think you've got
OL,19,Fthis wrong.
