OL,3,CScotland becoming more intolerant amid
OL,4,Cimmigration debate, warns Yousaf
OL,6,F"If politicians tell the good voters
OL,7,Fthat immigration is going to make
OL,8,Feveryone better off ` then people get
OL,9,Fworse off ` people start to ask, quite
OL,10,Frightly, serious questions."
